# URL Shortener API

A backend URL shortener project built with Node.js, Express.js, MySQL, and Redis.

## Features

- Create short URLs
- Redirect to original URLs
- Store URLs permanently in MySQL
- Track click analytics
- Cache redirect lookups using Redis
- View all stored URLs

## Tech Stack

- Node.js
- Express.js
- MySQL
- Redis
- dotenv

